Échantillonneur:

seeds <- function(nchain, init_alpha0, init_alpha1, init_alpha2, init_alpha12, init_sigma, init_b, prop_sd, x1, x2, N)
{
  
  alpha0 <- init_alpha0
  alpha1 <- init_alpha1
  alpha2 <- init_alpha2
  alpha12 <- init_alpha12
  sigma <- init_sigma
  b <- init_b
  
  p <- inv.logit(alpha0 + alpha1 * x1 + alpha2 * x2 + alpha12 * x1 * x2 + b)
  
  chain <- matrix(NA, nchain + 1, 5)
  chain_b <- matrix(NA, nchain + 1, N)
  
  chain[1,1] <- init_alpha0
  chain[1,2] <- init_alpha1
  chain[1,3] <- init_alpha2
  chain[1,4] <- init_alpha12
  chain[1,5] <- init_sigma
  chain_b[1,] <- init_b
  
  for (i in 1:nchain)
  {
    # Mise à jour de alpha0
    prop <- rnorm(1, alpha0, prop_sd[1])
    prop_p <- inv.logit(prop + alpha1 * x1 + alpha2 * x2 + alpha12 * x1 * x2 + b)
    
    top <- - ((prop^2) / (2 * 1e6)) + sum(r * log(prop_p)) + sum((n-r) * log(1 - prop_p))
    bottom <- - ((alpha0^2) / (2 * 1e6)) + sum(r * log(p)) + sum((n-r) * log(1 - p))
    
    acc_prob <- exp(top - bottom)
    
    if (!is.finite(acc_prob))
      browser()
    
    if (runif(1) < acc_prob){
      alpha0 <- prop
      p <- prop_p
    }
    
    # Mise à jour de alpha1
    prop <- rnorm(1, alpha1, prop_sd[2])
    prop_p <- inv.logit(alpha0 + prop * x1 + alpha2 * x2 + alpha12 * x1 * x2 + b)
    
    top <- - ((prop^2) / (2 * 1e6)) + sum(r * log(prop_p)) + sum((n-r) * log(1 - prop_p))
    bottom <- - ((alpha1^2) / (2 * 1e6)) + sum(r * log(p)) + sum((n-r) * log(1 - p))
    
    acc_prob <- exp(top - bottom)
    if (!is.finite(acc_prob))
      browser()
    
    if (runif(1) < acc_prob){
      alpha1 <- prop
      p <- prop_p
    }
    
    # Mise à jour de alpha2
    prop <- rnorm(1, alpha2, prop_sd[3])
    prop_p <- inv.logit(alpha0 + alpha1 * x1 + prop * x2 + alpha12 * x1 * x2 + b)
    
    top <- - ((prop^2) / (2 * 1e6)) + sum(r * log(prop_p)) + sum((n-r) * log(1 - prop_p))
    bottom <- - ((alpha2^2) / (2 * 1e6)) + sum(r * log(p)) + sum((n-r) * log(1 - p))
    
    acc_prob <- exp(top - bottom)
    if (!is.finite(acc_prob))
      browser()
    
    if (runif(1) < acc_prob){
      alpha2 <- prop
      p <- prop_p
    }
    
    # Mise à jour de alpha12
    prop <- rnorm(1, alpha12, prop_sd[4])
    prop_p <- inv.logit(alpha0 + alpha1 * x1 + alpha2 * x2 + prop * x1 * x2 + b)
    
    top <- - ((prop^2) / (2 * 1e6)) + sum(r * log(prop_p)) + sum((n-r) * log(1 - prop_p))
    bottom <- - ((alpha12^2) / (2 * 1e6)) + sum(r * log(p)) + sum((n-r) * log(1 - p))
    
    acc_prob <- exp(top - bottom)
    if (!is.finite(acc_prob))
      browser()
    
    if (runif(1) < acc_prob){
      alpha12 <- prop
      p <- prop_p
    }
    
    # Mise à jour de sigma
    sigma <- 1 / rgamma(1, 10^-3 + N / 2, 10^-3 + 0.5 * sum(b^2)) #change parameters
    
    # Mise à jour de la chaine
    chain[i+1,] <- c(alpha0, alpha1, alpha2, alpha12, sigma)
    
    # Mise à jour de b
    for (j in 1:N)
    {
      prop <- rnorm(1, b[j], prop_sd[6])
      prop_p_j <- inv.logit(alpha0 + alpha1 * x1[j] + alpha2 * x2[j] + alpha12 * x1[j] * x2[j] + prop)
      
      top <- - (prop^2 / (2 * sigma)) + r[j] * log(prop_p_j) + (n[j] - r[j]) * log(1 - prop_p_j)
      bottom <- - (b[j]^2 / (2 * sigma)) + r[j] * log(p[j]) + (n[j] - r[j]) * log(1 - p[j])
      
      acc_prob <- exp(top - bottom)
      if (!is.finite(acc_prob))
      browser()
      
      if (runif(1) < acc_prob){
        b[j] <- prop
        p[j] <- prop_p_j
      }
    }
    #Mise à jour de la chaine
    chain_b[i+1,] <- b
  }
  return(chain)
}
chain <- seeds(1e4, init_alpha0, init_alpha1, init_alpha2, init_alpha12, init_sigma, init_b, rep(0.2,6), x1, x2, N)
